      <title>【C&#43;&#43;】C&#43;&#43;中的设计模式</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/c&#43;&#43;c&#43;&#43;%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</link>
